	<br>
	<div style="text-align:right;">
		OYAMA, Letícia Akazaki<sup>1</sup>; MALAQUIAS, Mineia Alessandra Scaranello<sup>2</sup>; NORONHA, Lucia de<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa CNPq-PIBIC		<BR>
